<br>
Player A is sitting/standing/fighting/socializing/boozin'/etc<br>
<br>
Player B inspects Player A and asks to see Items 513, 012, and C52<br>
<br>
Player A being a nice guy/gal obliges Player B and puts said items into trade window<br>
<br>
Player B cancels the trade by &quot;accident&quot;<br>
<br>
Player A realizes that he/she didn't have any slots for the items (since they don't re-equip themselves) they drop to ground<br>
<br>
Player B makes off like a bandit-o<br>
<br>
